description: The home-grown Sputnik V vaccine, which is still undergoing mass testing, is being used.
title: Covid: Russia begins vaccinations in Moscow
title_page: Covid: Russia begins vaccinations in Moscow - BBC News
maintext: They were all calm enough about receiving Sputnik V, even though it's still undergoing mass trials to test its safety and efficacy. One doctor said she'd seen enough Covid patients at her own hospital to prefer taking her chances with the vaccine.
